      "type": "text",
      "text": "# Phase 2.1: 考试状态机 + 阅卷分配 + 质量监控 + 成绩发布设计\n\n> **创建**: 2026-03-30 10:53:10\n> **依赖**: Phase 1c (Capability + AuditLog) ✅。与 Phase 1d 无交叉依赖，可并行。\n> **范围**: 纯后端，不含前端页面\n> **总设计**: `docs/plans/2026-03-29-business-logic-backfill-design.md` §Phase 2\n> **业务参考**: `C:\\Users\\Administrator\\haofenshu-clone\\docs\\business-logic.md`（好分数考试流程）\n\n---\n\n## 1. 目标\n\n将考试生命周期从\"基础 5 态\"补全为\"完整 7 态 + 阅卷任务分配 + 质量监控 + 成绩发布\"，使 edu-cloud 具备：\n\n1. **完整考试状态机**：draft → scanning → grading → reviewing → completed → published → archived\n2. **题块级阅卷任务分配**：按题目将阅卷任务分配给不同教师（教育行业标准做法）\n3. **质量抽检机制**：随机抽样 + 一致性检查，保障阅卷质量\n4. **成绩发布流水线**：发布触发排名计算 + 错题更新 + 事件通知\n5. **Agent 工具**：3 个新工具，让 AI 助手能查询和管理阅卷进度\n\n## 2. 现状分析\n\n### 2.1 现有考试模型\n\n```python\n# modules/exam/service.py\n_VALID_STATUS_TRANSITIONS = {\n    \"draft\": {\"scanning\"},\n    \"scanning\": {\"grading\", \"draft\"},\n    \"grading\": {\"reviewing\"},\n    \"reviewing\": {\"completed\"},\n}\n```\n\n- Exam 5 态：draft → scanning → grading → reviewing → completed\n- completed 时自动触发 `run_full_pipeline()`（当前是 stub）\n- 无 `published` / `archived` 状态\n\n### 2.2 现有阅卷模型\n\n| 模型 | 说明 | 缺什么 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| GradingTask | AI 阅卷任务（整科级） | 无题块级分配 |\n| AIGradingResult | 单道题的 AI 评分结果 | 有 review_status 但无分配关系 |\n| TeacherReview | 教师审核记录（approve/override） | 只审 AI 结果，无独立阅卷 |\n| Rubric | 评分标准 | 完整 |\n\n**核心缺失**：没有\"哪个老师负责改哪些题\"的分配机制。当前流程是：AI 全部批改 → 教师逐个审核。缺乏人工阅卷和质量控制。\n\n### 2.3 好分数参考\n\n好分数的考试流程（从 `business-logic.md`）：\n- 阅卷任务按题目分配给教师（一个老师改一道或几道题）\n- 支持双评（同题两人独立评分）+ 仲裁\n- 阅卷完成后需要\"发布成绩\"操作，发布后学生/家长可见\n- 发布后自动生成各类统计报告\n\n**本次取舍**：\n- ✅ 题块级分配\n- ✅ 成绩发布流\n- ✅ 质量抽检\n- ❌ 双评+仲裁（v1 不做，数据模型预留扩展字段）\n- ❌ 前端页面（单独 Phase）\n\n## 3. 架构设计\n\n### 3.1 状态机扩展\n\n```\ndraft ──→ scanning ──→ grading ──→ reviewing ──→ completed ──→ published ──→ archived\n  ↑          │                                       │             │\n  └──────────┘ (可回退)                              │             │\n                                                     │             │\n                                              (前置条件检查)   (触发排名+错题)\n```\n\n**新增转换规则**：\n\n```python\n_VALID_STATUS_TRANSITIONS = {\n    \"draft\": {\"scanning\"},\n    \"scanning\": {\"grading\", \"draft\"},\n    \"grading\": {\"reviewing\"},\n    \"reviewing\": {\"completed\"},\n    # 新增\n    \"completed\": {\"published\"},\n    \"published\": {\"archived\"},\n}\n```\n\n**转换前置条件**：\n\n| 转换 | 前置条件 | 说明 |\n|------|---------|------|\n| completed → published | 所有 GradingAssignment status=completed | 所有阅卷任务完成 |\n| completed → published | 无 HIGH severity 质量问题未处理 | 质量检查通过 |\n| published → archived | 无 | 归档不设门槛 |\n\n**转换后触发**：\n\n| 转换 | 触发动作 | 说明 |\n|------|---------|------|\n| reviewing → completed | run_full_pipeline()（现有，保持不变） | AI 阅卷流水线（已是 stub） |\n| completed → published | publish_service.on_publish() | **新增**：排名计算 + 错题更新 + EventBus emit |\n| published → archived | 无 | 标记归档 |\n\n> **与现有 run_full_pipeline 的关系**：reviewing→completed 仍触发 run_full_pipeline()（现有逻辑不变，当前是 stub）。\n> completed→published 是**独立的新流程**，在 publish_service 中实现排名和错题逻辑。\n> 两者互不影响：completed 是\"阅卷完成\"，published 是\"成绩对外发布\"。\n\n### 3.2 数据模型\n\n#### GradingAssignment（题块级阅卷任务分配）\n\n```python\nclass GradingAssignment(Base, IdMixin, TimestampMixin):\n    __tablename__ = \"grading_assignments\"\n\n    exam_id: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(String(36), ForeignKey(\"exams.id\"), index=True)\n    subject_id: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(String(36), ForeignKey(\"subjects.id\"), index=True)\n    question_ids: Mapped[list] = mapped_column(JSON)\n        # 分配的题目 ID 列表，如 [\"q1-uuid\", \"q2-uuid\"]\n    assigned_to: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(String(36), ForeignKey(\"users.id\"), index=True)\n    status: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(String(20), default=\"pending\")\n        # \"pending\" → \"in_progress\" → \"completed\"\n    graded_count: Mapped[int] = mapped_column(default=0)\n        # 已批改的答卷数\n    total_count: Mapped[int] = mapped_column(default=0)\n        # 需要批改的总答卷数（分配时计算）\n    started_at: Mapped[Optional[datetime]] = mapped_column(nullable=True)\n    completed_at: Mapped[Optional[datetime]] = mapped_column(nullable=True)\n    school_id: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(String(36), ForeignKey(\"schools.id\"), index=True)\n\n    # 双评扩展预留（v1 不启用）\n    is_second_grading: Mapped[bool] = mapped_column(default=False)\n    paired_assignment_id: Mapped[Optional[str]] = mapped_column(\n        String(36), ForeignKey(\"grading_assignments.id\"), nullable=True\n    )\n\n    __table_args__ = (\n        Index(\"ix_assignment_exam_teacher\", \"exam_id\", \"assigned_to\"),\n    )\n```\n\n**状态转换**：\n```\npending ──(教师开始批改)──→ in_progress ──(全部批完)──→ completed\n```\n\n**设计决策**：\n- question_ids 用 JSON 列表而非关联表：一个分配通常 1-5 道题，JSON 更简洁\n- graded_count / total_count 用于进度计算，避免每次查询 count\n- 双评字段预留但 v1 不使用（is_second_grading 默认 False）\n\n#### GradingQualityCheck（质量抽检）\n\n```python\nclass GradingQualityCheck(Base, IdMixin, TimestampMixin):\n    __tablename__ = \"grading_quality_checks\"\n\n    exam_id: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(String(36), ForeignKey(\"exams.id\"), index=True)\n    subject_id: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(String(36), ForeignKey(\"subjects.id\"), index=True)\n    question_id: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(String(36), ForeignKey(\"questions.id\"))\n    check_type: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(String(20))\n        # \"sampling\" — 随机抽样复查\n        # \"consistency\" — 同一教师前后一致性\n        # \"deviation\" — AI 与人工评分偏差\n    original_result_id: Mapped[Optional[str]] = mapped_column(\n        String(36), ForeignKey(\"ai_grading_results.id\"), nullable=True\n    )\n        # 被抽检的原始结果（AI 结果或人工结果）\n    original_grader_id: Mapped[Optional[str]] = mapped_column(\n        String(36), ForeignKey(\"users.id\"), nullable=True\n    )\n        # 原始评分人\n    checker_id: Mapped[Optional[str]] = mapped_column(\n        String(36), ForeignKey(\"users.id\"), nullable=True\n    )\n        # 抽检人（复查的教师）\n    original_score: Mapped[float] = mapped_column()\n    check_score: Mapped[Optional[float]] = mapped_column(nullable=True)\n        # 抽检评分（复查后填入）\n    deviation: Mapped[Optional[float]] = mapped_column(nullable=True)\n        # |check_score - original_score|，审核后自动计算\n    severity: Mapped[Optional[str]] = mapped_column(String(10), nullable=True)\n        # \"low\" (偏差≤10%) / \"med\" (10-20%) / \"high\" (>20%)\n    status: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(String(20), default=\"pending\")\n        # \"pending\" → \"reviewed\"\n    comment: Mapped[Optional[str]] = mapped_column(Text, nullable=True)\n    school_id: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(String(36), ForeignKey(\"schools.id\"), index=True)\n```\n\n**抽检类型说明**：\n\n| 类型 | 触发方式 | 说明 |\n|------|---------|------|\n| sampling | 手动触发，按比例随机抽取已批改的答卷 | 最基础的质量控制 |\n| consistency | 手动触发，随机抽取同一教师的多份答卷检查评分一致性 | 检测评分标准漂移 |\n| deviation | 自动触发，AI 批改和人工批改同一道题，比较偏差 | 校准 AI 评分模型 |\n\n### 3.3 核心服务\n\n#### GradingAssignmentService（`modules/grading/assignment_service.py`）\n\n```python\nclass GradingAssignmentService:\n    @staticmethod\n    async def auto_assign(\n        db, exam_id, subject_id, teacher_ids: list[UUID], school_id\n    ) -> list[GradingAssignment]:\n        \"\"\"按题目 round-robin 分配给教师列表\"\"\"\n        # 1. 查询该科目的所有题目\n        questions = await get_questions_by_subject(db, subject_id)\n        # 2. 按题目数量均匀分配\n        chunks = round_robin_split(questions, len(teacher_ids))\n        # 3. 创建分配记录\n        assignments = []\n        for teacher_id, question_chunk in zip(teacher_ids, chunks):\n            # 4. 统计每道题需要批改的答卷数\n            total = await count_answers_for_questions(db, exam_id, question_chunk)\n            assignment = GradingAssignment(\n                exam_id=exam_id, subject_id=subject_id,\n                question_ids=[q.id for q in question_chunk],\n                assigned_to=teacher_id, total_count=total,\n                school_id=school_id,\n            )\n            assignments.append(assignment)\n        db.add_all(assignments)\n        await db.flush()\n        return assignments\n\n    @staticmethod\n    async def assign_block(\n        db, exam_id, subject_id, question_ids, teacher_id, school_id\n    ) -> GradingAssignment:\n        \"\"\"手动分配指定题目给指定教师\"\"\"\n        total = await count_answers_for_questions(db, exam_id, question_ids)\n        assignment = GradingAssignment(\n            exam_id=exam_id, subject_id=subject_id,\n            question_ids=question_ids, assigned_to=teacher_id,\n            total_count=total, school_id=school_id,\n        )\n        db.add(assignment)\n        await db.flush()\n        return assignment\n\n    @staticmethod\n    async def update_progress(db, assignment_id, graded_count) -> GradingAssignment:\n        \"\"\"更新批改进度，达到 total_count 自动转 completed\"\"\"\n        assignment = await db.get(GradingAssignment, assignment_id)\n        assignment.graded_count = graded_count\n        if assignment.status == \"pending\" and graded_count > 0:\n            assignment.status = \"in_progress\"\n            assignment.started_at = utc_now()\n        if graded_count >= assignment.total_count:\n            assignment.status = \"completed\"\n            assignment.completed_at = utc_now()\n        return assignment\n\n    @staticmethod\n    async def get_progress(db, exam_id) -> dict:\n        \"\"\"返回考试阅卷进度汇总\"\"\"\n        assignments = await list_by_exam(db, exam_id)\n        return {\n            \"total_assignments\": len(assignments),\n            \"completed\": sum(1 for a in assignments if a.status == \"completed\"),\n            \"in_progress\": sum(1 for a in assignments if a.status == \"in_progress\"),\n            \"pending\": sum(1 for a in assignments if a.status == \"pending\"),\n            \"total_papers\": sum(a.total_count for a in assignments),\n            \"graded_papers\": sum(a.graded_count for a in assignments),\n            \"progress_pct\": (\n                sum(a.graded_count for a in assignments)\n                / max(sum(a.total_count for a in assignments), 1)\n                * 100\n            ),\n            \"by_teacher\": [\n                {\n                    \"teacher_id\": str(a.assigned_to),\n                    \"status\": a.status,\n                    \"graded\": a.graded_count,\n                    \"total\": a.total_count,\n                    \"questions\": a.question_ids,\n                }\n                for a in assignments\n            ],\n        }\n```\n\n#### QualityCheckService（`modules/grading/quality_service.py`）\n\n```python\nclass QualityCheckService:\n    @staticmethod\n    async def create_sampling_checks(\n        db, exam_id, subject_id, rate: float = 0.1, school_id=None\n    ) -> list[GradingQualityCheck]:\n        \"\"\"随机抽样已批改结果的 rate 比例\"\"\"\n        # 1. 查询已完成的评分结果\n        results = await get_completed_results(db, exam_id, subject_id)\n        # 2. 随机抽取\n        import random\n        sample_size = max(1, int(len(results) * rate))\n        sampled = random.sample(results, min(sample_size, len(results)))\n        # 3. 创建抽检记录\n        checks = []\n        for result in sampled:\n            check = GradingQualityCheck(\n                exam_id=exam_id, subject_id=subject_id,\n                question_id=result.question_id,\n                check_type=\"sampling\",\n                original_result_id=result.id,\n                original_grader_id=result.grader_id,\n                original_score=result.score,\n                status=\"pending\", school_id=school_id,\n            )\n            checks.append(check)\n        db.add_all(checks)\n        await db.flush()\n        return checks\n\n    @staticmethod\n    async def review_check(\n        db, check_id, checker_id, check_score, comment=None\n    ) -> GradingQualityCheck:\n        \"\"\"审核抽检：填入复查分数，自动计算偏差和严重度\"\"\"\n        check = await db.get(GradingQualityCheck, check_id)\n        check.checker_id = checker_id\n        check.check_score = check_score\n        check.deviation = abs(check_score - check.original_score)\n        check.comment = comment\n        check.status = \"reviewed\"\n\n        # 计算严重度（基于题目满分的百分比）\n        max_score = await get_question_max_score(db, check.question_id)\n        if max_score > 0:\n            pct = check.deviation / max_score * 100\n            if pct <= 10:\n                check.severity = \"low\"\n            elif pct <= 20:\n                check.severity = \"med\"\n            else:\n                check.severity = \"high\"\n\n        return check\n\n    @staticmethod\n    async def get_quality_report(db, exam_id) -> dict:\n        \"\"\"生成质量报告\"\"\"\n        checks = await list_checks(db, exam_id)\n        reviewed = [c for c in checks if c.status == \"reviewed\"]\n        return {\n            \"total_checks\": len(checks),\n            \"reviewed\": len(reviewed),\n            \"pending\": len(checks) - len(reviewed),\n            \"avg_deviation\": (\n                sum(c.deviation for c in reviewed) / max(len(reviewed), 1)\n            ),\n            \"high_severity_count\": sum(\n                1 for c in reviewed if c.severity == \"high\"\n            ),\n            \"has_blocking_issues\": any(\n                c.severity == \"high\" and c.status == \"reviewed\"\n                for c in checks\n            ),\n            \"by_type\": {\n                t: {\n                    \"count\": sum(1 for c in reviewed if c.check_type == t),\n                    \"avg_deviation\": (\n                        sum(c.deviation for c in reviewed if c.check_type == t)\n                        / max(sum(1 for c in reviewed if c.check_type == t), 1)\n                    ),\n                }\n                for t in [\"sampling\", \"consistency\", \"deviation\"]\n            },\n        }\n```\n\n#### ExamPublishService（`modules/exam/publish_service.py`）\n\n```python\nclass ExamPublishService:\n    @staticmethod\n    async def publish(db, exam_id, school_id) -> dict:\n        \"\"\"发布考试成绩\"\"\"\n        exam = await db.get(Exam, exam_id)\n\n        # 前置条件 1: 状态必须是 completed\n        if exam.status != \"completed\":\n            raise StateError(f\"Cannot publish exam in status '{exam.status}'\")\n\n        # 前置条件 2: 所有阅卷任务已完成\n        assignments = await list_assignments(db, exam_id)\n        incomplete = [a for a in assignments if a.status != \"completed\"]\n        if incomplete:\n            raise StateError(\n                f\"{len(incomplete)} grading assignments not completed\"\n            )\n\n        # 前置条件 3: 无 HIGH severity 质量问题\n        report = await QualityCheckService.get_quality_report(db, exam_id)\n        if report[\"high_severity_count\"] > 0:\n            raise StateError(\n                f\"{report['high_severity_count']} high-severity quality issues unresolved\"\n            )\n\n        # 状态转换\n        exam.status = \"published\"\n\n        # 触发后续动作\n        await _calculate_rankings(db, exam_id, school_id)\n        await _update_error_books(db, exam_id, school_id)\n\n        # EventBus 通知（现有 events.py 基础设施）\n        from edu_cloud.core.events import event_bus\n        await event_bus.emit(\"exam.published\", {\n            \"exam_id\": str(exam_id),\n            \"school_id\": str(school_id),\n        })\n\n        return {\n            \"exam_id\": str(exam_id),\n            \"status\": \"published\",\n            \"rankings_calculated\": True,\n        }\n\n    @staticmethod\n    async def archive(db, exam_id):\n        \"\"\"归档考试\"\"\"\n        exam = await db.get(Exam, exam_id)\n        if exam.status != \"published\":\n            raise StateError(f\"Cannot archive exam in status '{exam.status}'\")\n        exam.status = \"archived\"\n\n    @staticmethod\n    async def _calculate_rankings(db, exam_id, school_id):\n        \"\"\"计算排名（按科目 + 总分）\"\"\"\n        subjects = await get_exam_subjects(db, exam_id)\n        for subject in subjects:\n            # 按科目排名\n            results = await get_subject_results(db, exam_id, subject.id)\n            sorted_results = sorted(results, key=lambda r: r.score, reverse=True)\n            for rank, result in enumerate(sorted_results, 1):\n                result.rank = rank\n\n        # 总分排名\n        total_scores = await get_total_scores(db, exam_id)\n        sorted_totals = sorted(total_scores, key=lambda t: t.total, reverse=True)\n        for rank, ts in enumerate(sorted_totals, 1):\n            ts.rank = rank\n\n    @staticmethod\n    async def _update_error_books(db, exam_id, school_id):\n        \"\"\"更新错题本（失分题自动加入）\"\"\"\n        # 查找失分率 > 50% 的题目+学生\n        results = await get_low_score_results(db, exam_id, threshold=0.5)\n        for result in results:\n            await upsert_error_book_entry(\n                db, student_id=result.student_id,\n                question_id=result.question_id,\n                exam_id=exam_id, school_id=school_id,\n                score=result.score, max_score=result.max_score,\n            )\n```\n\n### 3.4 API 设计\n\n#### 阅卷分配端点（`modules/grading/assignment_router.py`）\n\n| 方法 | 路径 | 权限 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| POST | `/api/v1/grading/assignments/auto` | MANAGE_GRADING | 自动分配（round-robin） |\n| POST | `/api/v1/grading/assignments` | MANAGE_GRADING | 手动分配 |\n| GET | `/api/v1/grading/assignments` | VIEW_GRADING | 列表（exam_id/assigned_to 过滤） |\n| PATCH | `/api/v1/grading/assignments/{id}` | MANAGE_GRADING | 更新状态/进度 |\n| GET | `/api/v1/grading/progress/{exam_id}` | VIEW_GRADING | 进度汇总 |\n\n**请求/响应示例**：\n\n```\nPOST /api/v1/grading/assignments/auto\n{\n    \"exam_id\": \"uuid\",\n    \"subject_id\": \"uuid\",\n    \"teacher_ids\": [\"uuid1\", \"uuid2\", \"uuid3\"]\n}\n→ 200: [{ \"id\": \"...\", \"assigned_to\": \"uuid1\", \"question_ids\": [...], \"total_count\": 120 }, ...]\n```\n\n```\nGET /api/v1/grading/progress/{exam_id}\n→ 200: {\n    \"total_assignments\": 9,\n    \"completed\": 6, \"in_progress\": 2, \"pending\": 1,\n    \"total_papers\": 3600, \"graded_papers\": 2400, \"progress_pct\": 66.7,\n    \"by_teacher\": [...]\n}\n```\n\n#### 质量监控端点（`modules/grading/quality_router.py`）\n\n| 方法 | 路径 | 权限 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| POST | `/api/v1/grading/quality-checks/sampling` | MANAGE_GRADING | 创建抽样检查 |\n| POST | `/api/v1/grading/quality-checks/consistency` | MANAGE_GRADING | 创建一致性检查 |\n| GET | `/api/v1/grading/quality-checks` | VIEW_GRADING | 列表（exam_id/status 过滤） |\n| POST | `/api/v1/grading/quality-checks/{id}/review` | MANAGE_GRADING | 提交审核 |\n| GET | `/api/v1/grading/quality-report/{exam_id}` | VIEW_GRADING | 质量报告 |\n\n#### 成绩发布端点（`modules/exam/router.py` 扩展）\n\n| 方法 | 路径 | 权限 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| POST | `/api/v1/exams/{id}/publish` | MANAGE_EXAM_RESULTS | 发布成绩（含前置检查） |\n| POST | `/api/v1/exams/{id}/archive` | MANAGE_EXAM_RESULTS | 归档考试 |\n\n### 3.5 权限扩展\n\n新增 Permission 枚举值：\n\n| 权限 | 角色 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| MANAGE_GRADING | platform_admin, academic_director | 分配阅卷任务、创建质量检查 |\n| VIEW_GRADING | 上述 + grade_leader, subject_teacher | 查看进度和质量报告 |\n| MANAGE_EXAM_RESULTS | platform_admin, academic_director | 发布/归档成绩 |\n\n### 3.6 Agent 工具\n\n```python\n@registry.register(\n    name=\"get_grading_progress\",\n    description=\"获取考试阅卷进度汇总：总任务数、完成/进行中/待开始、按教师明细\",\n    module_code=\"grading\",\n    domain=\"exam\",\n    risk_level=\"low\",\n    allowed_roles=None,  # 所有角色可查\n)\nasync def get_grading_progress(\n    exam_id: str,\n    _school_id: str = \"\",\n    _db=None,\n) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"使用现有的依赖注入模式（_db, _school_id），不用 AgentContext\"\"\"\n    ...\n\n@registry.register(\n    name=\"get_quality_report\",\n    description=\"获取阅卷质量报告：抽检数、偏差统计、高严重度问题数\",\n    module_code=\"grading\",\n    domain=\"exam\",\n    risk_level=\"low\",\n    allowed_roles=[\"platform_admin\", \"academic_director\"],\n)\nasync def get_quality_report(\n    exam_id: str,\n    _school_id: str = \"\",\n    _db=None,\n) -> dict:\n    ...\n\n@registry.register(\n    name=\"assign_grading_task\",\n    description=\"自动分配阅卷任务：按题目均匀分配给指定教师\",\n    module_code=\"grading\",\n    domain=\"exam\",\n    risk_level=\"med\",  # 写操作\n    allowed_roles=[\"platform_admin\", \"academic_director\"],\n)\nasync def assign_grading_task(\n    exam_id: str, subject_id: str, teacher_ids: str,\n    _school_id: str = \"\",\n    _db=None,\n) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"teacher_ids 为逗号分隔字符串（Agent 工具参数序列化限制）\"\"\"\n    ...\n```\n\n**注意**：这 3 个工具的 `@registry.register` 使用 Phase 1d 扩展后的元数据格式。如果 Phase 1d 尚未完成，暂用现有格式注册，后续 Phase 1d 统一升级。由于两个 Phase 并行执行，工具注册使用最小公共格式（现有 name + description），元数据字段由 Phase 1d Executor 统一添加。\n\n## 4. 文件清单\n\n| 操作 | 文件 | 职责 |\n|------|------|------|\n| Create | `src/edu_cloud/modules/grading/assignment_service.py` | 阅卷分配 Service |\n| Create | `src/edu_cloud/modules/grading/quality_service.py` | 质量检查 Service |\n| Create | `src/edu_cloud/modules/grading/assignment_router.py` | 分配 API |\n| Create | `src/edu_cloud/modules/grading/quality_router.py` | 质量检查 API |\n| Create | `src/edu_cloud/modules/exam/publish_service.py` | 成绩发布 Service |\n| Create | `src/edu_cloud/ai/tools/grading_ops.py` | 3 个 Agent 工具 |\n| Modify | `src/edu_cloud/modules/grading/models.py` | 新增 GradingAssignment + GradingQualityCheck |\n| Modify | `src/edu_cloud/modules/exam/service.py` | 扩展状态机（+published, +archived） |\n| Modify | `src/edu_cloud/modules/exam/router.py` | 新增 publish/archive 端点 |\n| Modify | `src/edu_cloud/core/permissions.py` | 新增 MANAGE_GRADING / VIEW_GRADING / MANAGE_EXAM_RESULTS |\n| Modify | `src/edu_cloud/api/app.py` | 注册新 router |\n| Modify | `src/edu_cloud/ai/tools/__init__.py` | 注册新工具模块 |\n| Modify | `alembic/env.py` | 导入新模型 |\n| Modify | `tests/conftest.py` | 导入新模型 |\n| Modify | `tests/test_alembic_migration.py` | 更新表集合 |\n| Modify | `CLAUDE.md` | 同步 API 端点 + 数据模型 + 权限 |\n\n## 5. 并行冲突分析（与 Phase 1d）\n\n| 共享文件 | Phase 1d 改什么 | Phase 2.1 改什么 | 冲突风险 |\n|---------|----------------|-----------------|---------|\n| `api/app.py` | 无直接改动（agent.py 内部重构） | 注册 assignment_router + quality_router | **无冲突** |\n| `ai/tools/__init__.py` | 修改工具元数据 | 添加 grading_ops import | **低**（不同行） |\n| `ai/registry.py` | 扩展 ToolSpec 字段 | 不改 | **无冲突** |\n| `core/permissions.py` | 不改 | 新增 3 个枚举 | **无冲突** |\n| `alembic/env.py` | 导入 agent_profile | 导入 grading 新模型 | **低**（不同 import 行） |\n| `tests/conftest.py` | 导入 agent_profile | 导入 grading 新模型 | **低**（不同 import 行） |\n| `CLAUDE.md` | Agent 架构段 | API 端点 + 模型段 | **低**（不同 section） |\n\n**结论**：两个 Phase 文件交叉极少，可安全并行。仅需在 merge 时处理 alembic/env.py 和 conftest.py 的 import 行合并（trivial）。\n\n**Agent 工具格式兼容**：Phase 2.1 的 3 个新工具暂用现有注册格式。Phase 1d 完成后由其 Executor 统一升级所有工具元数据（包括这 3 个新工具）。如果 Phase 1d 先完成，Phase 2.1 直接用新格式注册。\n\n## 6. 测试策略\n\n| 组件 | 测试重点 | 预估测试数 |\n|------|---------|-----------|\n| 状态机扩展 | published/archived 转换 + 前置条件阻塞 + 无效转换拒绝 | 6 |\n| GradingAssignment model | CRUD + 状态转换 + 唯一约束 | 4 |\n| auto_assign | round-robin 分配 + 题目数不整除 + 单教师 + 空题目 | 5 |\n| assign_block | 手动分配 + 重复分配检测 | 3 |\n| update_progress | 进度更新 + 自动完成 + 边界（0/total） | 4 |\n| get_progress | 进度汇总 + 空分配 + 全部完成 | 3 |\n| QualityCheck sampling | 抽样创建 + rate 边界 + 空结果集 | 4 |\n| QualityCheck review | 审核 + 偏差计算 + severity 分级 | 4 |\n| quality_report | 报告汇总 + 无检查 + 有 high severity | 3 |\n| publish | 前置条件全满足 + 任务未完成阻塞 + 质量问题阻塞 | 5 |\n| archive | 正常归档 + 非 published 状态阻塞 | 2 |\n| Assignment API | 5 端点 CRUD + 权限检查 | 6 |\n| Quality API | 5 端点 CRUD + 权限检查 | 5 |\n| Publish API | publish + archive 端点 + 错误响应 | 4 |\n| Agent 工具 | 3 工具 × 正常+异常 | 4 |\n| Alembic | 新表迁移 smoke test | 1 |\n\n**预估总计**: ~63 新测试\n\n## 7. 风险与缓解\n\n| 风险 | 级别 | 缓解 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 排名计算性能（大考试 1000+ 学生） | MED | 使用 SQL ORDER BY + ROW_NUMBER()，不在 Python 排序 |\n| 质量检查 high severity 阻塞发布 | LOW | API 返回明确错误信息，指出哪些检查需要处理 |\n| auto_assign 题目不整除 | LOW | 余数分配给第一个教师，测试覆盖 |\n| 与 Phase 1d 并行 merge 冲突 | LOW | 文件交叉少，仅 import 行级别冲突 |\n| Agent 工具格式兼容 | LOW | 暂用现有格式，Phase 1d 统一升级 |\n\n## 8. 不在范围内\n\n- 前端阅卷进度大屏页（→ 后续 Phase）\n- 双评+仲裁机制（数据模型已预留字段）\n- 考后分析报告自动生成（→ Phase 3.1）\n- 成绩导出（Excel/PDF）\n- 家长端成绩查看（→ Phase 3）\n"
    }
  ],
  "structuredContent": {
    "content": "# Phase 2.1: 考试状态机 + 阅卷分配 + 质量监控 + 成绩发布设计\n\n> **创建**: 2026-03-30 10:53:10\n> **依赖**: Phase 1c (Capability + AuditLog) ✅。与 Phase 1d 无交叉依赖，可并行。\n> **范围**: 纯后端，不含前端页面\n> **总设计**: `docs/plans/2026-03-29-business-logic-backfill-design.md` §Phase 2\n> **业务参考**: `C:\\Users\\Administrator\\haofenshu-clone\\docs\\business-logic.md`（好分数考试流程）\n\n---\n\n## 1. 目标\n\n将考试生命周期从\"基础 5 态\"补全为\"完整 7 态 + 阅卷任务分配 + 质量监控 + 成绩发布\"，使 edu-cloud 具备：\n\n1. **完整考试状态机**：draft → scanning → grading → reviewing → completed → published → archived\n2. **题块级阅卷任务分配**：按题目将阅卷任务分配给不同教师（教育行业标准做法）\n3. **质量抽检机制**：随机抽样 + 一致性检查，保障阅卷质量\n4. **成绩发布流水线**：发布触发排名计算 + 错题更新 + 事件通知\n5. **Agent 工具**：3 个新工具，让 AI 助手能查询和管理阅卷进度\n\n## 2. 现状分析\n\n### 2.1 现有考试模型\n\n```python\n# modules/exam/service.py\n_VALID_STATUS_TRANSITIONS = {\n    \"draft\": {\"scanning\"},\n    \"scanning\": {\"grading\", \"draft\"},\n    \"grading\": {\"reviewing\"},\n    \"reviewing\": {\"completed\"},\n}\n```\n\n- Exam 5 态：draft → scanning → grading → reviewing → completed\n- completed 时自动触发 `run_full_pipeline()`（当前是 stub）\n- 无 `published` / `archived` 状态\n\n### 2.2 现有阅卷模型\n\n| 模型 | 说明 | 缺什么 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| GradingTask | AI 阅卷任务（整科级） | 无题块级分配 |\n| AIGradingResult | 单道题的 AI 评分结果 | 有 review_status 但无分配关系 |\n| TeacherReview | 教师审核记录（approve/override） | 只审 AI 结果，无独立阅卷 |\n| Rubric | 评分标准 | 完整 |\n\n**核心缺失**：没有\"哪个老师负责改哪些题\"的分配机制。当前流程是：AI 全部批改 → 教师逐个审核。缺乏人工阅卷和质量控制。\n\n### 2.3 好分数参考\n\n好分数的考试流程（从 `business-logic.md`）：\n- 阅卷任务按题目分配给教师（一个老师改一道或几道题）\n- 支持双评（同题两人独立评分）+ 仲裁\n- 阅卷完成后需要\"发布成绩\"操作，发布后学生/家长可见\n- 发布后自动生成各类统计报告\n\n**本次取舍**：\n- ✅ 题块级分配\n- ✅ 成绩发布流\n- ✅ 质量抽检\n- ❌ 双评+仲裁（v1 不做，数据模型预留扩展字段）\n- ❌ 前端页面（单独 Phase）\n\n## 3. 架构设计\n\n### 3.1 状态机扩展\n\n```\ndraft ──→ scanning ──→ grading ──→ reviewing ──→ completed ──→ published ──→ archived\n  ↑          │                                       │             │\n  └──────────┘ (可回退)                              │             │\n                                                     │             │\n                                              (前置条件检查)   (触发排名+错题)\n```\n\n**新增转换规则**：\n\n```python\n_VALID_STATUS_TRANSITIONS = {\n    \"draft\": {\"scanning\"},\n    \"scanning\": {\"grading\", \"draft\"},\n    \"grading\": {\"reviewing\"},\n    \"reviewing\": {\"completed\"},\n    # 新增\n    \"completed\": {\"published\"},\n    \"published\": {\"archived\"},\n}\n```\n\n**转换前置条件**：\n\n| 转换 | 前置条件 | 说明 |\n|------|---------|------|\n| completed → published | 所有 GradingAssignment status=completed | 所有阅卷任务完成 |\n| completed → published | 无 HIGH severity 质量问题未处理 | 质量检查通过 |\n| published → archived | 无 | 归档不设门槛 |\n\n**转换后触发**：\n\n| 转换 | 触发动作 | 说明 |\n|------|---------|------|\n| reviewing → completed | run_full_pipeline()（现有，保持不变） | AI 阅卷流水线（已是 stub） |\n| completed → published | publish_service.on_publish() | **新增**：排名计算 + 错题更新 + EventBus emit |\n| published → archived | 无 | 标记归档 |\n\n> **与现有 run_full_pipeline 的关系**：reviewing→completed 仍触发 run_full_pipeline()（现有逻辑不变，当前是 stub）。\n> completed→published 是**独立的新流程**，在 publish_service 中实现排名和错题逻辑。\n> 两者互不影响：completed 是\"阅卷完成\"，published 是\"成绩对外发布\"。\n\n### 3.2 数据模型\n\n#### GradingAssignment（题块级阅卷任务分配）\n\n```python\nclass GradingAssignment(Base, IdMixin, TimestampMixin):\n    __tablename__ = \"grading_assignments\"\n\n    exam_id: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(String(36), ForeignKey(\"exams.id\"), index=True)\n    subject_id: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(String(36), ForeignKey(\"subjects.id\"), index=True)\n    question_ids: Mapped[list] = mapped_column(JSON)\n        # 分配的题目 ID 列表，如 [\"q1-uuid\", \"q2-uuid\"]\n    assigned_to: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(String(36), ForeignKey(\"users.id\"), index=True)\n    status: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(String(20), default=\"pending\")\n        # \"pending\" → \"in_progress\" → \"completed\"\n    graded_count: Mapped[int] = mapped_column(default=0)\n        # 已批改的答卷数\n    total_count: Mapped[int] = mapped_column(default=0)\n        # 需要批改的总答卷数（分配时计算）\n    started_at: Mapped[Optional[datetime]] = mapped_column(nullable=True)\n    completed_at: Mapped[Optional[datetime]] = mapped_column(nullable=True)\n    school_id: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(String(36), ForeignKey(\"schools.id\"), index=True)\n\n    # 双评扩展预留（v1 不启用）\n    is_second_grading: Mapped[bool] = mapped_column(default=False)\n    paired_assignment_id: Mapped[Optional[str]] = mapped_column(\n        String(36), ForeignKey(\"grading_assignments.id\"), nullable=True\n    )\n\n    __table_args__ = (\n        Index(\"ix_assignment_exam_teacher\", \"exam_id\", \"assigned_to\"),\n    )\n```\n\n**状态转换**：\n```\npending ──(教师开始批改)──→ in_progress ──(全部批完)──→ completed\n```\n\n**设计决策**：\n- question_ids 用 JSON 列表而非关联表：一个分配通常 1-5 道题，JSON 更简洁\n- graded_count / total_count 用于进度计算，避免每次查询 count\n- 双评字段预留但 v1 不使用（is_second_grading 默认 False）\n\n#### GradingQualityCheck（质量抽检）\n\n```python\nclass GradingQualityCheck(Base, IdMixin, TimestampMixin):\n    __tablename__ = \"grading_quality_checks\"\n\n    exam_id: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(String(36), ForeignKey(\"exams.id\"), index=True)\n    subject_id: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(String(36), ForeignKey(\"subjects.id\"), index=True)\n    question_id: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(String(36), ForeignKey(\"questions.id\"))\n    check_type: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(String(20))\n        # \"sampling\" — 随机抽样复查\n        # \"consistency\" — 同一教师前后一致性\n        # \"deviation\" — AI 与人工评分偏差\n    original_result_id: Mapped[Optional[str]] = mapped_column(\n        String(36), ForeignKey(\"ai_grading_results.id\"), nullable=True\n    )\n        # 被抽检的原始结果（AI 结果或人工结果）\n    original_grader_id: Mapped[Optional[str]] = mapped_column(\n        String(36), ForeignKey(\"users.id\"), nullable=True\n    )\n        # 原始评分人\n    checker_id: Mapped[Optional[str]] = mapped_column(\n        String(36), ForeignKey(\"users.id\"), nullable=True\n    )\n        # 抽检人（复查的教师）\n    original_score: Mapped[float] = mapped_column()\n    check_score: Mapped[Optional[float]] = mapped_column(nullable=True)\n        # 抽检评分（复查后填入）\n    deviation: Mapped[Optional[float]] = mapped_column(nullable=True)\n        # |check_score - original_score|，审核后自动计算\n    severity: Mapped[Optional[str]] = mapped_column(String(10), nullable=True)\n        # \"low\" (偏差≤10%) / \"med\" (10-20%) / \"high\" (>20%)\n    status: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(String(20), default=\"pending\")\n        # \"pending\" → \"reviewed\"\n    comment: Mapped[Optional[str]] = mapped_column(Text, nullable=True)\n    school_id: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(String(36), ForeignKey(\"schools.id\"), index=True)\n```\n\n**抽检类型说明**：\n\n| 类型 | 触发方式 | 说明 |\n|------|---------|------|\n| sampling | 手动触发，按比例随机抽取已批改的答卷 | 最基础的质量控制 |\n| consistency | 手动触发，随机抽取同一教师的多份答卷检查评分一致性 | 检测评分标准漂移 |\n| deviation | 自动触发，AI 批改和人工批改同一道题，比较偏差 | 校准 AI 评分模型 |\n\n### 3.3 核心服务\n\n#### GradingAssignmentService（`modules/grading/assignment_service.py`）\n\n```python\nclass GradingAssignmentService:\n    @staticmethod\n    async def auto_assign(\n        db, exam_id, subject_id, teacher_ids: list[UUID], school_id\n    ) -> list[GradingAssignment]:\n        \"\"\"按题目 round-robin 分配给教师列表\"\"\"\n        # 1. 查询该科目的所有题目\n        questions = await get_questions_by_subject(db, subject_id)\n        # 2. 按题目数量均匀分配\n        chunks = round_robin_split(questions, len(teacher_ids))\n        # 3. 创建分配记录\n        assignments = []\n        for teacher_id, question_chunk in zip(teacher_ids, chunks):\n            # 4. 统计每道题需要批改的答卷数\n            total = await count_answers_for_questions(db, exam_id, question_chunk)\n            assignment = GradingAssignment(\n                exam_id=exam_id, subject_id=subject_id,\n                question_ids=[q.id for q in question_chunk],\n                assigned_to=teacher_id, total_count=total,\n                school_id=school_id,\n            )\n            assignments.append(assignment)\n        db.add_all(assignments)\n        await db.flush()\n        return assignments\n\n    @staticmethod\n    async def assign_block(\n        db, exam_id, subject_id, question_ids, teacher_id, school_id\n    ) -> GradingAssignment:\n        \"\"\"手动分配指定题目给指定教师\"\"\"\n        total = await count_answers_for_questions(db, exam_id, question_ids)\n        assignment = GradingAssignment(\n            exam_id=exam_id, subject_id=subject_id,\n            question_ids=question_ids, assigned_to=teacher_id,\n            total_count=total, school_id=school_id,\n        )\n        db.add(assignment)\n        await db.flush()\n        return assignment\n\n    @staticmethod\n    async def update_progress(db, assignment_id, graded_count) -> GradingAssignment:\n        \"\"\"更新批改进度，达到 total_count 自动转 completed\"\"\"\n        assignment = await db.get(GradingAssignment, assignment_id)\n        assignment.graded_count = graded_count\n        if assignment.status == \"pending\" and graded_count > 0:\n            assignment.status = \"in_progress\"\n            assignment.started_at = utc_now()\n        if graded_count >= assignment.total_count:\n            assignment.status = \"completed\"\n            assignment.completed_at = utc_now()\n        return assignment\n\n    @staticmethod\n    async def get_progress(db, exam_id) -> dict:\n        \"\"\"返回考试阅卷进度汇总\"\"\"\n        assignments = await list_by_exam(db, exam_id)\n        return {\n            \"total_assignments\": len(assignments),\n            \"completed\": sum(1 for a in assignments if a.status == \"completed\"),\n            \"in_progress\": sum(1 for a in assignments if a.status == \"in_progress\"),\n            \"pending\": sum(1 for a in assignments if a.status == \"pending\"),\n            \"total_papers\": sum(a.total_count for a in assignments),\n            \"graded_papers\": sum(a.graded_count for a in assignments),\n            \"progress_pct\": (\n                sum(a.graded_count for a in assignments)\n                / max(sum(a.total_count for a in assignments), 1)\n                * 100\n            ),\n            \"by_teacher\": [\n                {\n                    \"teacher_id\": str(a.assigned_to),\n                    \"status\": a.status,\n                    \"graded\": a.graded_count,\n                    \"total\": a.total_count,\n                    \"questions\": a.question_ids,\n                }\n                for a in assignments\n            ],\n        }\n```\n\n#### QualityCheckService（`modules/grading/quality_service.py`）\n\n```python\nclass QualityCheckService:\n    @staticmethod\n    async def create_sampling_checks(\n        db, exam_id, subject_id, rate: float = 0.1, school_id=None\n    ) -> list[GradingQualityCheck]:\n        \"\"\"随机抽样已批改结果的 rate 比例\"\"\"\n        # 1. 查询已完成的评分结果\n        results = await get_completed_results(db, exam_id, subject_id)\n        # 2. 随机抽取\n        import random\n        sample_size = max(1, int(len(results) * rate))\n        sampled = random.sample(results, min(sample_size, len(results)))\n        # 3. 创建抽检记录\n        checks = []\n        for result in sampled:\n            check = GradingQualityCheck(\n                exam_id=exam_id, subject_id=subject_id,\n                question_id=result.question_id,\n                check_type=\"sampling\",\n                original_result_id=result.id,\n                original_grader_id=result.grader_id,\n                original_score=result.score,\n                status=\"pending\", school_id=school_id,\n            )\n            checks.append(check)\n        db.add_all(checks)\n        await db.flush()\n        return checks\n\n    @staticmethod\n    async def review_check(\n        db, check_id, checker_id, check_score, comment=None\n    ) -> GradingQualityCheck:\n        \"\"\"审核抽检：填入复查分数，自动计算偏差和严重度\"\"\"\n        check = await db.get(GradingQualityCheck, check_id)\n        check.checker_id = checker_id\n        check.check_score = check_score\n        check.deviation = abs(check_score - check.original_score)\n        check.comment = comment\n        check.status = \"reviewed\"\n\n        # 计算严重度（基于题目满分的百分比）\n        max_score = await get_question_max_score(db, check.question_id)\n        if max_score > 0:\n            pct = check.deviation / max_score * 100\n            if pct <= 10:\n                check.severity = \"low\"\n            elif pct <= 20:\n                check.severity = \"med\"\n            else:\n                check.severity = \"high\"\n\n        return check\n\n    @staticmethod\n    async def get_quality_report(db, exam_id) -> dict:\n        \"\"\"生成质量报告\"\"\"\n        checks = await list_checks(db, exam_id)\n        reviewed = [c for c in checks if c.status == \"reviewed\"]\n        return {\n            \"total_checks\": len(checks),\n            \"reviewed\": len(reviewed),\n            \"pending\": len(checks) - len(reviewed),\n            \"avg_deviation\": (\n                sum(c.deviation for c in reviewed) / max(len(reviewed), 1)\n            ),\n            \"high_severity_count\": sum(\n                1 for c in reviewed if c.severity == \"high\"\n            ),\n            \"has_blocking_issues\": any(\n                c.severity == \"high\" and c.status == \"reviewed\"\n                for c in checks\n            ),\n            \"by_type\": {\n                t: {\n                    \"count\": sum(1 for c in reviewed if c.check_type == t),\n                    \"avg_deviation\": (\n                        sum(c.deviation for c in reviewed if c.check_type == t)\n                        / max(sum(1 for c in reviewed if c.check_type == t), 1)\n                    ),\n                }\n                for t in [\"sampling\", \"consistency\", \"deviation\"]\n            },\n        }\n```\n\n#### ExamPublishService（`modules/exam/publish_service.py`）\n\n```python\nclass ExamPublishService:\n    @staticmethod\n    async def publish(db, exam_id, school_id) -> dict:\n        \"\"\"发布考试成绩\"\"\"\n        exam = await db.get(Exam, exam_id)\n\n        # 前置条件 1: 状态必须是 completed\n        if exam.status != \"completed\":\n            raise StateError(f\"Cannot publish exam in status '{exam.status}'\")\n\n        # 前置条件 2: 所有阅卷任务已完成\n        assignments = await list_assignments(db, exam_id)\n        incomplete = [a for a in assignments if a.status != \"completed\"]\n        if incomplete:\n            raise StateError(\n                f\"{len(incomplete)} grading assignments not completed\"\n            )\n\n        # 前置条件 3: 无 HIGH severity 质量问题\n        report = await QualityCheckService.get_quality_report(db, exam_id)\n        if report[\"high_severity_count\"] > 0:\n            raise StateError(\n                f\"{report['high_severity_count']} high-severity quality issues unresolved\"\n            )\n\n        # 状态转换\n        exam.status = \"published\"\n\n        # 触发后续动作\n        await _calculate_rankings(db, exam_id, school_id)\n        await _update_error_books(db, exam_id, school_id)\n\n        # EventBus 通知（现有 events.py 基础设施）\n        from edu_cloud.core.events import event_bus\n        await event_bus.emit(\"exam.published\", {\n            \"exam_id\": str(exam_id),\n            \"school_id\": str(school_id),\n        })\n\n        return {\n            \"exam_id\": str(exam_id),\n            \"status\": \"published\",\n            \"rankings_calculated\": True,\n        }\n\n    @staticmethod\n    async def archive(db, exam_id):\n        \"\"\"归档考试\"\"\"\n        exam = await db.get(Exam, exam_id)\n        if exam.status != \"published\":\n            raise StateError(f\"Cannot archive exam in status '{exam.status}'\")\n        exam.status = \"archived\"\n\n    @staticmethod\n    async def _calculate_rankings(db, exam_id, school_id):\n        \"\"\"计算排名（按科目 + 总分）\"\"\"\n        subjects = await get_exam_subjects(db, exam_id)\n        for subject in subjects:\n            # 按科目排名\n            results = await get_subject_results(db, exam_id, subject.id)\n            sorted_results = sorted(results, key=lambda r: r.score, reverse=True)\n            for rank, result in enumerate(sorted_results, 1):\n                result.rank = rank\n\n        # 总分排名\n        total_scores = await get_total_scores(db, exam_id)\n        sorted_totals = sorted(total_scores, key=lambda t: t.total, reverse=True)\n        for rank, ts in enumerate(sorted_totals, 1):\n            ts.rank = rank\n\n    @staticmethod\n    async def _update_error_books(db, exam_id, school_id):\n        \"\"\"更新错题本（失分题自动加入）\"\"\"\n        # 查找失分率 > 50% 的题目+学生\n        results = await get_low_score_results(db, exam_id, threshold=0.5)\n        for result in results:\n            await upsert_error_book_entry(\n                db, student_id=result.student_id,\n                question_id=result.question_id,\n                exam_id=exam_id, school_id=school_id,\n                score=result.score, max_score=result.max_score,\n            )\n```\n\n### 3.4 API 设计\n\n#### 阅卷分配端点（`modules/grading/assignment_router.py`）\n\n| 方法 | 路径 | 权限 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| POST | `/api/v1/grading/assignments/auto` | MANAGE_GRADING | 自动分配（round-robin） |\n| POST | `/api/v1/grading/assignments` | MANAGE_GRADING | 手动分配 |\n| GET | `/api/v1/grading/assignments` | VIEW_GRADING | 列表（exam_id/assigned_to 过滤） |\n| PATCH | `/api/v1/grading/assignments/{id}` | MANAGE_GRADING | 更新状态/进度 |\n| GET | `/api/v1/grading/progress/{exam_id}` | VIEW_GRADING | 进度汇总 |\n\n**请求/响应示例**：\n\n```\nPOST /api/v1/grading/assignments/auto\n{\n    \"exam_id\": \"uuid\",\n    \"subject_id\": \"uuid\",\n    \"teacher_ids\": [\"uuid1\", \"uuid2\", \"uuid3\"]\n}\n→ 200: [{ \"id\": \"...\", \"assigned_to\": \"uuid1\", \"question_ids\": [...], \"total_count\": 120 }, ...]\n```\n\n```\nGET /api/v1/grading/progress/{exam_id}\n→ 200: {\n    \"total_assignments\": 9,\n    \"completed\": 6, \"in_progress\": 2, \"pending\": 1,\n    \"total_papers\": 3600, \"graded_papers\": 2400, \"progress_pct\": 66.7,\n    \"by_teacher\": [...]\n}\n```\n\n#### 质量监控端点（`modules/grading/quality_router.py`）\n\n| 方法 | 路径 | 权限 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| POST | `/api/v1/grading/quality-checks/sampling` | MANAGE_GRADING | 创建抽样检查 |\n| POST | `/api/v1/grading/quality-checks/consistency` | MANAGE_GRADING | 创建一致性检查 |\n| GET | `/api/v1/grading/quality-checks` | VIEW_GRADING | 列表（exam_id/status 过滤） |\n| POST | `/api/v1/grading/quality-checks/{id}/review` | MANAGE_GRADING | 提交审核 |\n| GET | `/api/v1/grading/quality-report/{exam_id}` | VIEW_GRADING | 质量报告 |\n\n#### 成绩发布端点（`modules/exam/router.py` 扩展）\n\n| 方法 | 路径 | 权限 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| POST | `/api/v1/exams/{id}/publish` | MANAGE_EXAM_RESULTS | 发布成绩（含前置检查） |\n| POST | `/api/v1/exams/{id}/archive` | MANAGE_EXAM_RESULTS | 归档考试 |\n\n### 3.5 权限扩展\n\n新增 Permission 枚举值：\n\n| 权限 | 角色 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| MANAGE_GRADING | platform_admin, academic_director | 分配阅卷任务、创建质量检查 |\n| VIEW_GRADING | 上述 + grade_leader, subject_teacher | 查看进度和质量报告 |\n| MANAGE_EXAM_RESULTS | platform_admin, academic_director | 发布/归档成绩 |\n\n### 3.6 Agent 工具\n\n```python\n@registry.register(\n    name=\"get_grading_progress\",\n    description=\"获取考试阅卷进度汇总：总任务数、完成/进行中/待开始、按教师明细\",\n    module_code=\"grading\",\n    domain=\"exam\",\n    risk_level=\"low\",\n    allowed_roles=None,  # 所有角色可查\n)\nasync def get_grading_progress(\n    exam_id: str,\n    _school_id: str = \"\",\n    _db=None,\n) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"使用现有的依赖注入模式（_db, _school_id），不用 AgentContext\"\"\"\n    ...\n\n@registry.register(\n    name=\"get_quality_report\",\n    description=\"获取阅卷质量报告：抽检数、偏差统计、高严重度问题数\",\n    module_code=\"grading\",\n    domain=\"exam\",\n    risk_level=\"low\",\n    allowed_roles=[\"platform_admin\", \"academic_director\"],\n)\nasync def get_quality_report(\n    exam_id: str,\n    _school_id: str = \"\",\n    _db=None,\n) -> dict:\n    ...\n\n@registry.register(\n    name=\"assign_grading_task\",\n    description=\"自动分配阅卷任务：按题目均匀分配给指定教师\",\n    module_code=\"grading\",\n    domain=\"exam\",\n    risk_level=\"med\",  # 写操作\n    allowed_roles=[\"platform_admin\", \"academic_director\"],\n)\nasync def assign_grading_task(\n    exam_id: str, subject_id: str, teacher_ids: str,\n    _school_id: str = \"\",\n    _db=None,\n) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"teacher_ids 为逗号分隔字符串（Agent 工具参数序列化限制）\"\"\"\n    ...\n```\n\n**注意**：这 3 个工具的 `@registry.register` 使用 Phase 1d 扩展后的元数据格式。如果 Phase 1d 尚未完成，暂用现有格式注册，后续 Phase 1d 统一升级。由于两个 Phase 并行执行，工具注册使用最小公共格式（现有 name + description），元数据字段由 Phase 1d Executor 统一添加。\n\n## 4. 文件清单\n\n| 操作 | 文件 | 职责 |\n|------|------|------|\n| Create | `src/edu_cloud/modules/grading/assignment_service.py` | 阅卷分配 Service |\n| Create | `src/edu_cloud/modules/grading/quality_service.py` | 质量检查 Service |\n| Create | `src/edu_cloud/modules/grading/assignment_router.py` | 分配 API |\n| Create | `src/edu_cloud/modules/grading/quality_router.py` | 质量检查 API |\n| Create | `src/edu_cloud/modules/exam/publish_service.py` | 成绩发布 Service |\n| Create | `src/edu_cloud/ai/tools/grading_ops.py` | 3 个 Agent 工具 |\n| Modify | `src/edu_cloud/modules/grading/models.py` | 新增 GradingAssignment + GradingQualityCheck |\n| Modify | `src/edu_cloud/modules/exam/service.py` | 扩展状态机（+published, +archived） |\n| Modify | `src/edu_cloud/modules/exam/router.py` | 新增 publish/archive 端点 |\n| Modify | `src/edu_cloud/core/permissions.py` | 新增 MANAGE_GRADING / VIEW_GRADING / MANAGE_EXAM_RESULTS |\n| Modify | `src/edu_cloud/api/app.py` | 注册新 router |\n| Modify | `src/edu_cloud/ai/tools/__init__.py` | 注册新工具模块 |\n| Modify | `alembic/env.py` | 导入新模型 |\n| Modify | `tests/conftest.py` | 导入新模型 |\n| Modify | `tests/test_alembic_migration.py` | 更新表集合 |\n| Modify | `CLAUDE.md` | 同步 API 端点 + 数据模型 + 权限 |\n\n## 5. 并行冲突分析（与 Phase 1d）\n\n| 共享文件 | Phase 1d 改什么 | Phase 2.1 改什么 | 冲突风险 |\n|---------|----------------|-----------------|---------|\n| `api/app.py` | 无直接改动（agent.py 内部重构） | 注册 assignment_router + quality_router | **无冲突** |\n| `ai/tools/__init__.py` | 修改工具元数据 | 添加 grading_ops import | **低**（不同行） |\n| `ai/registry.py` | 扩展 ToolSpec 字段 | 不改 | **无冲突** |\n| `core/permissions.py` | 不改 | 新增 3 个枚举 | **无冲突** |\n| `alembic/env.py` | 导入 agent_profile | 导入 grading 新模型 | **低**（不同 import 行） |\n| `tests/conftest.py` | 导入 agent_profile | 导入 grading 新模型 | **低**（不同 import 行） |\n| `CLAUDE.md` | Agent 架构段 | API 端点 + 模型段 | **低**（不同 section） |\n\n**结论**：两个 Phase 文件交叉极少，可安全并行。仅需在 merge 时处理 alembic/env.py 和 conftest.py 的 import 行合并（trivial）。\n\n**Agent 工具格式兼容**：Phase 2.1 的 3 个新工具暂用现有注册格式。Phase 1d 完成后由其 Executor 统一升级所有工具元数据（包括这 3 个新工具）。如果 Phase 1d 先完成，Phase 2.1 直接用新格式注册。\n\n## 6. 测试策略\n\n| 组件 | 测试重点 | 预估测试数 |\n|------|---------|-----------|\n| 状态机扩展 | published/archived 转换 + 前置条件阻塞 + 无效转换拒绝 | 6 |\n| GradingAssignment model | CRUD + 状态转换 + 唯一约束 | 4 |\n| auto_assign | round-robin 分配 + 题目数不整除 + 单教师 + 空题目 | 5 |\n| assign_block | 手动分配 + 重复分配检测 | 3 |\n| update_progress | 进度更新 + 自动完成 + 边界（0/total） | 4 |\n| get_progress | 进度汇总 + 空分配 + 全部完成 | 3 |\n| QualityCheck sampling | 抽样创建 + rate 边界 + 空结果集 | 4 |\n| QualityCheck review | 审核 + 偏差计算 + severity 分级 | 4 |\n| quality_report | 报告汇总 + 无检查 + 有 high severity | 3 |\n| publish | 前置条件全满足 + 任务未完成阻塞 + 质量问题阻塞 | 5 |\n| archive | 正常归档 + 非 published 状态阻塞 | 2 |\n| Assignment API | 5 端点 CRUD + 权限检查 | 6 |\n| Quality API | 5 端点 CRUD + 权限检查 | 5 |\n| Publish API | publish + archive 端点 + 错误响应 | 4 |\n| Agent 工具 | 3 工具 × 正常+异常 | 4 |\n| Alembic | 新表迁移 smoke test | 1 |\n\n**预估总计**: ~63 新测试\n\n## 7. 风险与缓解\n\n| 风险 | 级别 | 缓解 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 排名计算性能（大考试 1000+ 学生） | MED | 使用 SQL ORDER BY + ROW_NUMBER()，不在 Python 排序 |\n| 质量检查 high severity 阻塞发布 | LOW | API 返回明确错误信息，指出哪些检查需要处理 |\n| auto_assign 题目不整除 | LOW | 余数分配给第一个教师，测试覆盖 |\n| 与 Phase 1d 并行 merge 冲突 | LOW | 文件交叉少，仅 import 行级别冲突 |\n| Agent 工具格式兼容 | LOW | 暂用现有格式，Phase 1d 统一升级 |\n\n## 8. 不在范围内\n\n- 前端阅卷进度大屏页（→ 后续 Phase）\n- 双评+仲裁机制（数据模型已预留字段）\n- 考后分析报告自动生成（→ Phase 3.1）\n- 成绩导出（Excel/PDF）\n- 家长端成绩查看（→ Phase 3）\n"
  }
}
