**发现**

1. `F-02`  
Severity: High  
Category: `code-bug`  
Evidence: `publish/archive` 确实改成通过 `get_exam(..., school_id=...)` 做归属校验了，[2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:1046](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:1046)；但同一份 plan 又明确保留了 API 层“缺少 school_id scope 检查”，[2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:1279](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:1279)。另外 `list_assignments/get_progress` 只按 `exam_id` 查，不带 `school_id` 过滤，[2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:631](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:631)；工具层也明确写了“未做 school_id scope 过滤”，[2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:1439](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:1439)。  
Impact: 这不是“已修复”，而是只修了 `publish/archive` 一条路径。阅卷进度、质量报告、Agent 工具仍可能出现跨校读取或操作。  
Suggested action: 把 `school_id` 贯穿到 assignment/quality service、router、tool 三层，并补 API/tool 的跨校访问测试。

2. `F-06`  
Severity: High  
Category: `code-bug`  
Evidence: `assign_block` 仍然保留 `total_count: int = 0` 默认值，[2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:573](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:573)；而手动分配 API 的请求体并没有 `total_count`，也没有“服务内自动统计答卷数”的步骤，[2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:1169](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:1169)。  
Impact: 手动创建的分配任务仍可能落成 `total_count=0`，随后被 `update_progress` 直接判定完成，进而污染进度统计和发布前置条件。  
Suggested action: 不要让调用方传 `total_count`。应在 service 内按 `exam_id + question_ids` 计算，或至少把它设为必填并校验 `> 0`。

3. `F-01`  
Severity: Medium  
Category: `design-concern`  
Evidence: plan 已改成 `published/archived` 只能通过 `ExamPublishService` 进入，并明确“不加入 `_VALID_STATUS_TRANSITIONS`”，[2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:232](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:232)；但 design 仍把 `completed -> published` 和 `published -> archived` 写进 `_VALID_STATUS_TRANSITIONS`，[2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-design.md:77](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-design.md:77)。  
Impact: 执行者如果按 design 落地，会把 Round 1 的 PATCH 绕过问题重新带回来。  
Suggested action: 统一 design 与 plan，明确 `update_exam` 永远拒绝 `published/archived`，状态进入只能走 `ExamPublishService`。

4. `F-04`  
Severity: Medium  
Category: `design-concern`  
Evidence: design 仍把 `completed -> published` 定义为“排名计算 + 错题更新 + EventBus emit”，[2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-design.md:103](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-design.md:103)，并给出了具体实现草图，[2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-design.md:435](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-design.md:435)。但 plan 中 `_calculate_rankings` 和 `_update_error_books` 仍是纯日志 stub，[2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:1076](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:1076) [2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:1091](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:1091)。  
Impact: “发布成功”但没有任何实际后续业务效果，和文档承诺不一致。  
Suggested action: 要么本 Phase 落一个最小可用实现，要么把 design/goal 明确降级为“仅预留 hook，不保证业务副作用”。

5. `F-07`  
Severity: Medium  
Category: `test-gap`  
Evidence: 测试契约虽然补上了模板，但关键修复点仍没有对应断言。API 测试只覆盖 happy path 和权限，[2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:1226](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:1226) [2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:1281](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:1281)，而同页又承认缺少 school scope，[2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:1279](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:1279)。工具测试也只校验注册和基础 category，[2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:1317](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:1317) [2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:1441](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:1441)。  
Impact: 当前最敏感的修复点仍可能在没有测试拦截的情况下回归。  
Suggested action: 补 4 类测试：跨校访问、手动分配 `total_count` 计算、publish 后置 hook 调用、重复分配拒绝。

6. `N-01`  
Severity: Medium  
Category: `code-bug`  
Evidence: design 的测试策略写了 `assign_block` 需要“重复分配检测”，[2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-design.md:623](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-design.md:623)；但 plan 的审查清单明确承认“assign_block 不检查重复分配”，[2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:684](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:684)。  
Impact: 同一题块可被重复派发，进度、工作量、发布前置条件都会失真。  
Suggested action: 增加重叠题块校验，至少限制同一 `exam_id + subject_id + question_ids` 不能重复分配给多个未归档任务。

7. `N-02`  
