1. `F-02`  
Severity: High  
Category: `code-bug`  
Evidence: `publish/archive` 确实改成通过 `get_exam(..., school_id=...)` 做归属校验了，[2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:1046](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:1046)；但同一份 plan 又明确保留了 API 层“缺少 school_id scope 检查”，[2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:1279](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:1279)。另外 `list_assignments/get_progress` 只按 `exam_id` 查，不带 `school_id` 过滤，[2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:631](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:631)；工具层也明确写了“未做 school_id scope 过滤”，[2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:1439](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:1439)。  
Impact: 这不是“已修复”，而是只修了 `publish/archive` 一条路径。阅卷进度、质量报告、Agent 工具仍可能出现跨校读取或操作。  
Suggested action: 把 `school_id` 贯穿到 assignment/quality service、router、tool 三层，并补 API/tool 的跨校访问测试。

2. `F-06`  
Severity: High  
Category: `code-bug`  
Evidence: `assign_block` 仍然保留 `total_count: int = 0` 默认值，[2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:573](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:573)；而手动分配 API 的请求体并没有 `total_count`，也没有“服务内自动统计答卷数”的步骤，[2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:1169](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md:1169)。  
Impact: 手动创建的分配任务仍可能落成 `total_count=0`，随后被 `update_progress` 直接判定完成，进而污染进度统计和发布前置条件。  
Suggested action: 不要让调用方传 `total_count`。应在 service 内按 `exam_id + question_ids` 计算，或至少把它设为必填并校验 `> 0`。

